        "section_title": "",
        "section_sub": "",
        "description": "<p>Sofia Alves has cool girl syndrome! She effortlessly excels in anything she sets her mind to. From painting, to art installations, to custom bags, to unique prints and patterns she creates for freelancing fashion opportunities. She does it all. She literally opened the doors from her iconic house at sunny Lisbon to our team, and became one of our favourite people who ever had the pleasure to work with. Aligned with her creative, independent and fearless spirit she was yet another match to the story that we want to share with you, our community.</p><p><br/></p><p>We catched up with Sofia and want everyone to know more about her. Click our quick interview below.</p>",
        "section_url": ""
      }
    },
    "cdaee2a8-d358-4577-8fe9-9de9843a1e92": {
      "type": "custom-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "template--18600182677848__cdaee2a8-d358-4577-8fe9-9de9843a1e92-1682015242266f3219-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Q: What made you eagerly accept the invitation to be a Paez face in 2023?</strong></p><p><br/><strong>A: </strong>Honestly, I jumped on the opportunity, driven by my love for the brand and the exciting possibilities that collaborations like this bring. The chance to synergize and create something amazing with Paez was too good to pass up!</p><p><em><strong><br/>Q: </strong></em><strong>How has Paez become an integral part of your life? Any favorite models?</strong></p><p><br/><strong>A:</strong> Paez has become a staple among my friends, both guys and girls. While I never bought them without reason, once I tried them on, I understood why everyone has a pair—they are incredibly comfortable. My favorite has to be the Moc's because they are versatile and always add a touch of beauty to any situation.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "template--18600182677848__cdaee2a8-d358-4577-8fe9-9de9843a1e92-1682015242266f3219-1"
