    "ac86e1fa-1121-43b3-90c7-bf1ca4009b0a": {
      "type": "custom-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "139e407d-9b47-4873-bcde-613e5f702443": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em><strong>Q: </strong></em><strong>Paez is all about \"walking the talk.\" How do you embody this motto in your life? Do you have a personal motto that guides you?</strong></p><p><br/><strong>A: </strong>As someone who works independently, this motto resonates deeply with me. Every day, we rely on our determination and willpower to make things happen. While I don't have a specific motto, I believe in pursuing what we love, embracing both good and challenging days. It's the challenges that make every achievement worthwhile. </p><p><em><strong><br/>Q: </strong></em><strong>You have experience collaborating with fashion brands. Can you share a project that held special meaning for you</strong><em><strong>?</strong></em></p><p><br/><strong>A:</strong> One aspect of my brand involves creating patterns and personalizing products for other brands. One of my most cherished projects was a collaboration with Burberry. I had the freedom to create two captivating canvases for their store and collection launch. Additionally, I got to add my artistic touch to their bags. The experience allowed me to showcase my artistic identity and express myself fully.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
