    "1d00efee-2f32-4ede-825d-e9560467cdce": {
      "type": "custom-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "6d10740f-f585-407b-ac7d-cec6189d36bb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em><strong>Q: </strong></em><strong>As an artist, how do you stay motivated and inspired?</strong></p><p><br/><strong>A: </strong>Inspiration stems from thorough research, exploring what others are creating, and delving into self-reflection and personal emotions. Inspiration is all around us, often unnoticed. On the motivation front, it's about taking action and getting things done, no matter how challenging the day might be. However, I also believe in taking breaks for contemplation, rest, and rejuvenation, which ultimately fuels renewed motivation.</p><p><em><strong><br/>Q: </strong></em><strong>Paez celebrates individuality and unique styles. How do you see your art and designs aligning with this spirit?</strong></p><p><br/><strong>A:</strong> I consider myself fortunate to be acknowledged as an individual. When creating my own pieces, I try not to focus too much on trends or what others are doing. The fact that the public and brands show interest in my work confirms that staying true to my own intuition and identity is valuable. My canvases, illustrations, and other creations are a genuine reflection of who I am and what I stand for—a testament to my various attempts and experiences.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "6d10740f-f585-407b-ac7d-cec6189d36bb"
